          "settings": {
            "label": "Distribution & manufacturing",
            "title": "More control under the hood. Fewer surprises on the shelf.",
            "description": "<p>250,000 square feet of fulfillment across California and Texas, $8-10M in active on-site inventory, and a Shenzhen manufacturing arm operating since 1999 - handling mold creation, injection molding, assembly, packaging, testing, and production oversight under one roof. Fewer handoffs, cleaner timelines, more control from product development to delivery.</p>",
